      <bpmn:documentation>IMPORTANT - Customer Contact, missing required info:
When a customer contact is opened and the user task cannot proceed, the user "unclaims" the task and the priority is set to a low value. 
On receipt of a customer contact answer, we are going to increase the priority of all declaration related user tasks to a high value. </bpmn:documentation>
